ABOUT ME
Hi! I'm John Wetzel.
I am a designer, engineer, researcher, entrepreneur, adventurer, and photographer. I am passionate about building a better world through human centered design, and I strive to create a positive impact on every community that I invest myself in.  
Curious about what drives creativity, I am constantly reminding myself and others of my favorite phrase: "Stop Consuming, Start Creating."  When I'm not working on projects, I'm trying out new technology products or I'm somewhere in the woods as far away from technology as possible. 
I am currently a Venture for America Fellow. I work 9-5 as the Lead Designer at BoxCast, a live video streaming startup in Cleveland, Ohio. From 5-9, I can be found working on any number of side projects. 
Lets work together.
Contact me: johnswetzel@gmail.com.
